      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "IDs must be {full_repo_relative_stem}_{entity}, using every directory level and not just the immediate parent, so semantic-extraction IDs deterministically match AST-extractor IDs and never create orphan ghost-duplicate nodes."
